---
Source:
  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 389
Tags:
  - Combat-Action=Pilgrimage-Descent Into Hell=The Inner Pilgrimage
By: Bâyazîd al-Bistâmî
---
On my first pilgrimage I saw only the temple; the second time, I saw
both the temple and the Lord of the temple; and the third time I saw
the Lord alone.
